  "title_en": "Greenland's natural mountains in Denmark",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">格陵兰，这个位于北大西洋的巨大岛屿，是丹麦王国的自治领地，以其壮丽的自然风光和独特的极地景观而闻名。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Greenland, a vast island in the North Atlantic, is an autonomous territory of the Kingdom of Denmark, known for its magnificent natural scenery and unique polar landscapes.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">格陵兰的大部分地区被厚厚的冰盖覆盖，这些冰盖不仅塑造了岛屿的地貌，也孕育了无数的冰川和峡湾。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Most areas of Greenland are covered by thick ice sheets, which not only shape the geography of the island but also give birth to countless glaciers and fjords.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">在这里，你可以体验到极昼和极夜的自然奇观，感受极地的宁静与神秘。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Here, you can experience the natural wonders of the midnight sun and polar night, feeling the tranquility and mystery of the polar regions.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">格陵兰的山脉和高原是徒步旅行和登山的理想之地，同时也是观赏野生动物的绝佳场所。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The mountains and plateaus of Greenland are ideal for hiking and mountaineering, and also excellent places to observe wildlife.</p>",
