  "title_cn": "因特拉肯",
  "title_en": "Interlaken",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">因特拉肯是瑞士中部的一个小镇，位于图恩湖和布里恩茨湖之间，是瑞士阿尔卑斯山旅游的起点。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Interlaken is a small town in central Switzerland, located between Lake Thun and Lake Brienz, and is the starting point for Swiss Alps tourism.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">这个小镇以其壮丽的山景和户外活动而闻名，如徒步、滑雪和滑翔伞。</p><p class=\"word-en\">This small town is known for its magnificent mountain views and outdoor activities such as hiking, skiing, and paragliding.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">作为前往少女峰的重要门户之一，因特拉肯吸引着世界各地的游客。</p><p class=\"word-en\">As one of the important gateways to the Jungfrau, Interlaken attracts tourists from all over the world.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">在这里，每一步都是探索，每一眼都是惊喜，因特拉肯等待着你的发现。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Here, every step is an exploration, every glance a delight; Interlaken awaits your discovery.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">你可以乘坐火车或缆车前往周围的山峰，如少女峰、雪朗峰和僧侣峰，体验阿尔卑斯山的壮丽。</p><p class=\"word-en\">You can take a train or cable car to the surrounding peaks, such as the Jungfrau, Schilthorn, and Mönch, to experience the splendor of the Alps.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">此外，因特拉肯也是体验瑞士传统乡村生活的绝佳之地，你可以在这里品尝地道的瑞士美食，感受当地人的热情好客。</p><p class=\"word-en\">In addition, Interlaken is an excellent place to experience traditional Swiss rural life, where you can taste authentic Swiss cuisine and feel the warmth and hospitality of the locals.</p>",
  "descr_en": "",
  "adress_cn": "瑞士",
  "adress_en": "Switzerland",
