11:{
  "title_cn": "瑞士阿尔卑斯山",
  "title_en": "The Alps in Switzerland",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">瑞士阿尔卑斯山，被誉为瑞士之魂，是一片古老而神秘的土地，其壮丽的自然风光和丰富的文化底蕴令人向往。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Swiss Alps, known as the soul of Switzerland, is an ancient and mystical land with magnificent natural scenery and rich cultural heritage that is highly sought after.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">这片山脉占据了瑞士60%的国土面积，是欧洲最年轻、最大、最高的山脉，其平均海拔3000米，拥有100多座海拔超过4000米的高峰。</p><p class=\"word-en\">This mountain range covers 60% of Switzerland's land area and is the youngest, largest, and highest mountain range in Europe, with an average altitude of 3000 meters and more than 100 peaks over 4000 meters.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">阿尔卑斯山不仅是自然爱好者的天堂，也是户外运动的圣地，提供了徒步、滑雪、攀岩等多种活动。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Alps is not only a paradise for nature lovers but also a holy land for outdoor sports, offering a variety of activities such as hiking, skiing, and climbing.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">这里的风景如画，从马特洪峰的雄伟到少女峰的秀丽，每一座山峰都有其独特的魅力和传说。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The scenery here is picturesque, from the majesty of the Matterhorn to the beauty of the Jungfrau, each peak has its unique charm and legends.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">阿尔卑斯山的冰川和雪景也是一大亮点，尤其是阿莱奇冰川，作为世界自然遗产，展示了大自然的神奇和力量。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The glaciers and snowscapes of the Alps are also a highlight, especially the Aletsch Glacier, which, as a World Natural Heritage site, showcases the magic and power of nature.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">此外，阿尔卑斯山也是欧洲文化的摇篮，历史上许多文学、艺术和音乐大师都曾在此留下足迹。</p><p class=\"word-en\">In addition, the Alps is also the cradle of European culture, where many literary, artistic, and musical masters have left their marks throughout history.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">无论是寻求自然的宁静，还是体验极限的刺激，瑞士阿尔卑斯山都是一个完美的目的地。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Whether you are seeking the tranquility of nature or the thrill of extreme sports, the Swiss Alps is a perfect destination.</p>",
  "descr_en": "",
  "adress_cn": "瑞士",
  "adress_en": "Switzerland",
  "img": "img/11.jpg",
  "country_flag_img": "flag/switzerland.jpg"
},
