  "title_en": "Karnak Temple",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">卡纳克神庙位于埃及卢克索，是古埃及最大的宗教建筑群之一，拥有3000多年的历史。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Karnak Temple is located in Luxor, Egypt, and is one of the largest religious complexes in ancient Egypt, with a history of over 3000 years.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">神庙以其巨大的石柱和精美的浮雕而著称，是研究古埃及历史和文化的重要遗址。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The temple is known for its huge stone columns and exquisite reliefs, making it an important site for studying the history and culture of ancient Egypt.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">卡纳克神庙是埃及旅游的必游之地，每年吸引着大量的游客和考古学家。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Karnak Temple is a must-visit place for tourism in Egypt, attracting a large number of tourists and archaeologists every year.</p>",
