  "title_en": "French Polynesia",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">法属波利尼西亚是南太平洋的一组群岛，包括著名的大溪地岛，以其清澈的海水和迷人的海滩而闻名。</p><p class=\"word-en\">French Polynesia is a group of islands in the South Pacific, including the famous Tahiti Island, known for its clear waters and charming beaches.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">这里是一个理想的度假胜地，适合进行潜水、帆船和放松。</p><p class=\"word-en\">It is an ideal vacation destination suitable for diving, sailing, and relaxation.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">法属波利尼西亚的自然风光和独特的文化使其成为世界著名的旅游目的地。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The natural scenery and unique culture of French Polynesia make it a world-renowned tourist destination.</p>",
