  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">阿布扎比酋长国宫酒店位于阿拉伯联合酋长国的首都阿布扎比，是一座豪华的五星级酒店。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Emirates Palace is located in Abu Dhabi, the capital of the United Arab Emirates, and is a luxurious five-star hotel.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">酒店以其宏伟的建筑和金碧辉煌的装饰而著称，被誉为中东地区最奢华的酒店之一。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The hotel is known for its magnificent architecture and splendid decoration, and is known as one of the most luxurious hotels in the Middle East.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">阿布扎比酋长国宫酒店不仅是一个住宿的地方，也是游客体验阿拉伯文化和奢华生活的好去处。</p><p class=\"word-en\">Emirates Palace is not only a place to stay but also a good place for tourists to experience Arab culture and luxurious life.</p>",
