  "title_en": "Sydney Opera House",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">悉尼歌剧院是澳大利亚最著名的地标之一，位于悉尼港的便利朗角。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Sydney Opera House is one of the most famous landmarks in Australia, located on Bennelong Point in Sydney Harbour.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">这座独特的建筑以其帆船形状的设计而闻名，是20世纪最具标志性的建筑之一。</p><p class=\"word-en\">This unique building is known for its sail-like design and is one of the most iconic buildings of the 20th century.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">悉尼歌剧院不仅是表演艺术的中心，也是世界文化遗产。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Sydney Opera House is not only a center for the performing arts but also a UNESCO World Heritage site.</p>",
