  "title_en": "Namib Desert",
  "descr_cn": "<p class=\"word-cn\">纳米布沙漠位于纳米比亚的南部，是世界上最古老的沙漠之一。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Namib Desert is located in the south of Namibia and is one of the oldest deserts in the world.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">沙漠以其红色的沙丘和独特的野生动物而闻名，是摄影师和自然爱好者的天堂。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The desert is known for its red sand dunes and unique wildlife, making it a paradise for photographers and nature enthusiasts.</p><p class=\"word-cn\">纳米布沙漠也是多个自然保护区的所在地，包括著名的索苏斯维利盐田。</p><p class=\"word-en\">The Namib Desert is also home to several nature reserves, including the famous Sossusvlei salt pans.</p>",
